  "profile": {
    "id": "u03_rohan",
    "user_name": "Rohan",
    "profession": "Bank PO aspirant",
    "mother_tongue": "Bengali",
    "interests": "Football, Bengali cinema, photography",
    "engagement": "chatty",
    "english_level": "A2",
    "personality": "enthusiastic, makes more grammar slips, talks about football a lot"
  },
  "transcript": [
    {
      "turn": 1,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Rohan, I hope you're feeling better today after the sleepless night. Did you get a chance to try the rule of thirds in your football photography?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Yeah, I tried it a little. It's kina hard to focus on the rule while the game is going fast. My phone camera not that good, but I try. Did you watch the Manchester United match last night? Their defense was really bad."
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You said it perfectly that time! Good try, and yes, I watched that match. I agree — their defense looked weak. What did you think about their attack? Was it better?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Their attack was okay, but too many passes went wrong. I think Bruno Fernandes was trying hard but couldn’t find the right player. Oh, and by the way, have you seen the new Shahrukh Khan movie? I heard it’s really good!"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi, nice to hear you watched the match carefully. I agree, passes were not good. I have not seen the new Shahrukh movie, but I like his old films. Will you go see it?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Yeah, I think I will go see it. Shahrukh is a big star in my country, and his movies always have a good story. I love his old films too — *Dilwale Dulhania Le Jayenge* is a classic! But, sorry, I'm a bit lonely these days, so I just want to talk about more things. How do you spend your free time when you feel bored?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You said “I think I will go see it” — perfect sentence! Glad you enjoy his films. When I’m bored, I sip chai and scroll through old photo albums. What do you do when you want to relax?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "When I feel lonely or bored, I usually watch Bengali movies or take my camera and walk around. Sometimes I play old football matches on my phone. It pass the time. But I miss my friends — they are busy with their own life. Do you ever feel lonely? What do you do then?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You said “It pass the time” — small fix: “It passes the time.” I get it, life gets busy. When I feel lonely, I call my sister or read old letters. What kinds of Bengali movies do you like best?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I like emotional Bengali movies — the kind with good stories and sad moments. My favorite actor is Prosenjit Chatterjee. He's been in so many hit films. I get really into them. But I also like action movies sometimes. Oh, and I take photos during rainy days — the light is nice. But I miss my friends. I think I should go now. Talk to you soon, Maya."
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You said “I take photos during rainy days” — perfect! Rainy day photos are so pretty. I hope you meet your friends soon. Talk to you again, Rohan. Take care!"
    }
  ],
